<p style="color: #c90431; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 22px; margin-top: 6px; margin-bottom: 6px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">Dear Honeywell Customer,</span> </strong></p>
<p style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 4px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 14px;"><span style="color: black;">Over the past two months we&rsquo;ve shared with you </span>our plans to upgrade our SAP systems at four R&amp;O sites &ndash; Tempe, Arizona; Wichita, Kansas; Basingstoke, UK, and Shanghai, China. We<span style="color: black;"> are excited to say that we are on track for the Aug. 6th, 2015, transition date.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p style="color: #c90431; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 6px; margin-bottom: 6px;"><strong>Just a quick reminder:</strong></p>
<table border="0" width="650" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
<tbody>
<tr>
