<td valign="top" width="578">
<ul style="margin-top: 10px;">
<li style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 10px;">Starting on July 31st, 2015, at 5:00pm (MST) through Aug. 6th,<strong> Honeywell will be unable to process new or existing R&amp;O orders and product shipments.</strong> Orders received during this time will be placed in a queue for processing after Aug. 6th.</li>
<li style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 10px;">Orders received before and after this time frame may experience up to a two-week turnaround delay.</li>
<li style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 10px;">The Estimated Ship Date (ESD) function in the MyAerospace.com customer portal will not operate during this time, and will not reflect updated shipping data until the transition is complete.</li>
<li style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 10px;">For all Aircraft on Ground (AOG) issues, please contact the Honeywell AOG Team at 1-800-601-3099 (US/Canada) or 1-602-365-3099 (International), select phone option #4.</li>
</ul>
